						<summary>

						<p>This is much damaged. It seems to record some endowment made by one <hi rend="bold">Raṇamuka-Nāraṇaṉ</hi> for feeding Brāhmaṇas (in the temple on the hill) on the day of his natal star Rōhiṇi in the Māśi month.</p>						

